dvbsplit : split programs from an MPEG TS stream into separate files
Author : Guy Martin <gmsoft@tuxicoman.be>


Building from svn :
-------------------
autoreconf -f -i
./configure
make && make install

Dependencies :
--------------
You need libdvbpsi to parse the PSI tables from the MPEG stream.

Running it :
------------
First, tune to the right frequency using czap or any similar application.
Then run dvbsplit on the right dvb adapter.
See `dvbsplit --help` for more details.

